query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `pdiIntelligentDetails` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `planId` int NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  `strategicContext` text,
  `durationMonths` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 24,
  `mentorId` int,
  `sponsorId1` int,
  `sponsorId2` int,
  `guardianId` int,
  `currentProfile` JSON NULL,
  `targetProfile` JSON NULL,
  `gapsAnalysis` JSON NULL,
  `milestone12Months` text,
  `milestone24Months` text,
  `milestone12Status` enum('pendente','concluido','atrasado') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pendente',
  `milestone24Status` enum('pendente','concluido','atrasado') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pendente',
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `pdiIntelligentDetails_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `pdiIntelligentDetails_planId_pdiPlans_id_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`planId`) REFERENCES `pdiPlans`(`id`) ON DELETE cascade ON UPDATE no action
);
